public class ImageBuilder extends Object implements Builder<Image>
ImageBuilder
Example to create an instance using the builder pattern 

     Image image = Image.builder()
             .url("{url}")
             .dimensions(dimensionsBuilder -> dimensionsBuilder)
             .build()
